ABOUT US
We drive home one single message:
Collaborative Creation is Multiplication
Karunachal is a for purpose non-profit organisation that is
committed to empowering youth and enabling leaders.
Karunachal is not just an organisation.
We are a movement that silently echoes the slogan
We the Youth, By the Youth, For the Youth.
We provide opportunity for experiential learning to provide the required exposure for a child to
think for himself or herself and grow in the direction of his or her natural inclination. We are not
trying to fight the traditional education system but rather run with it for creating a long term
change - together
Karunachal was born with the intention to unite communities from the coastal plains to the snow
capped mountains. With 600 million youth in the country we believe that only youth will
determine the future of the world
Our Vision
To enable youth to be more conscious and responsible future global citizens
Our Mission
To create rich, multi faceted and continually evolving programs using experiential learning tools
where youth learn about themselves, develop vital skills and realise their intellectual potential
and leadership capabilities to the fullest.
Values that
guide us
Co-Creation
Universal Love
Service
K CAMPS
Most youth are not empowered/enabled enough to take collective
ownership/action with the existing education systems.Immersion
programs are a cost effective tool which can help in learning and
provide higher transfer of knowledge to the child through hands-
on experience which can help the child make faster, quicker,
creative and more responsible decisions.
We provide a platform where youngsters from all social backgrounds
get an equal opportunity to participate in our own specially designed
immersion programs to build on their personal, social and
entrepreneurial skills. We attempt to enable the youth to make more
responsible and rational choices.
Our first flagship programme that includes immersive residential and non-
residential camps (K Camps) enables children to learn and explore about
Self, Environment & Entrepreneurship.
VOLUNTEER
Knowledge not only grows but multiplies when you share. Transform the lives of young children in
your community by volunteering your time for one year. Have fun while you learn and grow in the
areas of environment, entrepreneurship and exploration.Choose to volunteer in public relations,
operations, fundraising or human resource.
